<li><i><a href="/w/index.php?title=Apocalypse_and_the_writings_on_Revelation&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Apocalypse and the writings on Revelation (page does not exist)">Apocalypse and the writings on Revelation</a></i> (1931) edited by Mara Kalnins, Cambridge University Press, 1980, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0521224071" class="internal">ISBN 0-521-22407-1</a>, His last book touching on primitive symbolism, <a href="/wiki/Paganism" title="Paganism">paganism</a> and pre-<a href="/wiki/Christianity" title="Christianity">Christian</a> religion</li>
